item.description:
What could be better than a free outdoor concert on a breezy summer evening!

Holliston is starting their outdoor concert series TONIGHT from 6:30pm - 8:30pm. Come join us!

Look for a brown and pink chair, and a black baseball cap that says "Big Brothers, Big Sisters.

You can bring your own snacks and the Girl Scouts will be selling some as well. There's also a plentitude of places on 126 where you can grab a bite.

See you then!

Directions: Goodwill Park is on Green Street, which is directly off of Rte 16 (also known as Rte 126) in the center of town. If you're coming from Rte 495, take a left onto Green St....from Natick or Rte 128, take a right onto Green St. The park should be right there. In case you can't find me, my cell is 508-574-1115.
item.name: Free Summer Concert in Holliston tonight, June 28
